SUMMARY:GENTING BERHAD — Virtual Call #1
DESCRIPTION:Virtual only\nIssuer: GENTING BERHAD\nRoadshow: https://www.covacap.com/s/ddfcf3da5e820f754f274be945aaa214\n\nDeal context:\nGenting Berhad\, a Malaysian conglomerate\, is conducting a Non-Deal Roadshow with fixed income investor meetings organized by Deutsche Bank\, J.P. Morgan\, Barclays\, and Citi across virtual and Singapore-based sessions on April 13-15\, 2026. Senior management including CEO Dato' Sri Tan Kong Han and CFO Wong Yee Fun will participate. No specific bond terms have been announced — this is a pre-deal investor engagement at the Mandate stage.
LOCATION:Conference Call
